      "id": "Route228NorthHouse_Text_RewardWithUltimateMove",
      "en_US": [
        "Your quest for power has brought\n",
        "you here...\r",
        "...Very well.\r",
        "Let me reward your passion with some\n",
        "absolutely astounding moves.\r",
        "They’re the ultimate moves!\n",
        "Shall I teach them to your Pokémon?"
      ]
